How to plot an F distribution
x<- rnorm(1000)
y<- rnorm(1000)
plot(x,y)

plot(x, df(x,10,2)) # df(x, df1, df2, ncp, log = FALSE)

plot(x, df(x,10,20))

plot(x, df(x,10,200))
